          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Provider:</strong> Modal (serverless GPU cloud)</li>
            <li><strong>Models:</strong> Self-host any OSS LLM (vLLM/SGLang/TensorRT-LLM)</li>
